title: Conclusive list of best N64 games, in order
body:
1. Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time
2. Super Smash Bros.
3. Perfect Dark
4. Turok 2: Seeds of Evil
5. Mario Kart 64
6. Donkey Kong 64
7. Star Wars Episode I: Racer
8. Goldeneye
9. Legend of Zelda: Majora's Mask
10. Star Fox 64

Honorable mention to Jet Force Gemini

no backtalk
